    <item>
      <title>日元下跌，债券期货上涨，因日本央行推迟公布债务购买细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行表示将减少债务购买规模但将细节推迟至下次政策会议后，日元走弱，日本主权债券期货飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/yen-drops-as-boj-says-to-specify-bond-buying-plan-at-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:34:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行将在 7 月份详细说明债券购买规模削减情况，维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行维持基准利率不变，并表示将在7月份会议上制定减少债券购买规模的计划，同时在此之前维持债券购买规模不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国50年期特别债券发行需求强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/china-s-50-year-special-bond-sale-expected-to-draw-solid-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国债券市场的狂热丝毫没有减弱的迹象，中国期限最长的特别政府债券在拍卖会上获得了超出预期的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/china-s-50-year-special-bond-sale-expected-to-draw-solid-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 01:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下滑，日元因日本央行债券决定而下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本股市飙升之后，亚洲股市缩减了跌幅，而在日本央行决定推迟减少债券购买量之后，日元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
